<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>tạyb ạ̉nạ wndmạn</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1 (tạyb ạ̉nạ wndmạn .. btwsl ạlgẖfrạn
 kẖạṭy ạ̉nạ wgẖlṭạn .. wbʿmry mạ rḍytk
 sạmḥny ʿlly fạt .. yạmạ mrq ạ̉wqạt
 bạ̉fkạry wạlklmạt .. bạʿrf ạ̉nạ ʿṣytk)2
 ạạlqrạr- (rạjʿ lk gẖslny bdmk .. bdy tṣyr ʿlyã rạḍy
 ậmnt wṣdqtk ạ̉nk .. qạdr tmḥy kl ạlmạḍy)2
 2- mn dwnk mạ fyã ʿysẖ .. mtl ạlnsr ạlly mạlh rysẖ
 tʿbt mn ktr ạltftysẖ .. ʿly̱ mʿny̱ ạlhnạ
 jrbt ạlʿysẖẗ blạk .. fkrt bạqdr ạ̉nsạk
 gẖlṭt sạmḥny btrjạk .. rạjʿ lk ạ̉nạ
 3- ạlʿạlm trkny mjrwḥ .. mdẖlwl wksyr ạlrwḥ
 lgẖyrk lmyn bạrwḥ .. wʿndk ạlḥyạẗ
 md ly ạ̹ydk dạwyny .. ạ̉ḥḍny yạ ḥbyby wʿzyny
 ạ̹nt ạlly bdmk sẖạryny .. ʿ ṣlyb ạlnjạẗ</lyrics>
